title: Oomph! - 2014 - Die Englische Liedsammlung
description:
A collection of songs from Oomph! where they sing in English.
I haven't included any tracks from their album Truth or Dare.

All encoded at about 210Kbps vbr.

I have also made some covers to go with this. I am not a graphic artist (or any sort of artist) but can use GIMP to a fairly competent level.
